00:38:48,267 --> 00:38:49,186
It's okay.

654
00:38:51,947 --> 00:38:54,867
I met Lin Rulan before.

655
00:38:56,947 --> 00:38:58,466
About seven years ago,

656
00:38:59,267 --> 00:39:01,546
when she and Wu Lian were in court,

657
00:39:01,867 --> 00:39:03,106
she hired a litigator.

658
00:39:03,986 --> 00:39:06,986
But when I went to Yanyu Tower
to deliver silk threads the day before,

659
00:39:07,586 --> 00:39:10,787
I saw that litigator being brought
into Wu Lian's study.

660
00:39:12,827 --> 00:39:14,626
I've kept this

661
