to myself.

662
00:39:17,666 --> 00:39:21,347
A few days ago, when I saw the petition,

663
00:39:22,146 --> 00:39:23,586
I felt uneasy.

664
00:39:24,546 --> 00:39:26,026
I always felt guilty for her.

665
00:39:30,666 --> 00:39:32,347
I was so naive back then.

666
00:39:33,347 --> 00:39:34,747
I thought I could save her.

667
00:39:38,827 --> 00:39:40,707
Now that you know the ins and outs,

668
00:39:41,506 --> 00:39:43,466
if you don't want to get involved,

669
00:39:43,907 --> 00:39:45,106
I will have no complaints.

670
00:39:47,146 --> 00:39:48,227
Madame Xu.

671
00:39:49,066 --> 00:39:50,106
Though I value profit,

672
00:39:50,586 --> 00:39:52,387
don't belittle me.

673
00:39:52,907 --> 00:39:55,466
I've been able to support the women
in Huangji Embroidery House,

674
00:39:56,907 --> 00:39:58,066
and hide the embroideresses

675
00:39:58,347 --> 00:40:00,626
who escaped here for so many years.

676
00:40:01,026 --> 00:40:02,387
Do you think

677
00:40:02,586 --> 00:40:03,546
I only care about money?

678
00:40:06,026 --> 00:40:07,347
You're an upright woman.

679
00:40:08,106 --> 00:40:09,267
I misspoke.

680
00:40:15,794 --> 00:40:18,482
(Peace)

681
00:40:29,347 --> 00:40:30,186
Meng Wan.

682
00:40:31,026 --> 00:40:32,106
Long time no see.

683
00:40:33,026 --> 00:40:34,267
How have you been?

684
00:40:44,986 --> 00:40:45,986
I'm an idiot.

685
00:40:47,066 --> 00:40:49,146
I've been deceived for so long.

686
00:40:50,066 --> 00:40:51,347
Gu Songju.

687
00:40:51,986 --> 00:40:53,947
This name must have a deeper meaning.

688
00:40:54,666 --> 00:40:56,546
Just cut to the chase.

689
00:40:58,227 --> 00:40:59,707
I once heard a poem.

690
00:41:00,986 --> 00:41:02,506
There is a line in it.

691
00:41:03,066 --> 00:41:04,506
May my heart be as firm as an orchid

692
00:41:05,066 --> 00:41:06,586
to keep my promise.

693
00:41:07,066 --> 00:41:08,186
Have you heard it?

694
00:41:08,466 --> 00:41:09,586
Of course.

695
00:41:10,907 --> 00:41:12,506
Have a heart as firm as an orchid

696
00:41:12,907 --> 00:41:14,387
and keep my promise.

697
00:41:14,907 --> 00:41:16,186
That's exactly my intention.

698
00:41:18,026 --> 00:41:20,787
I underestimated your friendship
with Lin Rulan.

699
00:41:22,186 --> 00:41:24,986
The first time I saw you,

700
00:41:25,747 --> 00:41:27,626
I just thought you looked familiar.

701
00:41:28,827 --> 00:41:32,307
When you saw the embroidery samples
with Mrs. Ning,

702
00:41:32,586 --> 00:41:35,787
I took a good look at your face.

703
00:41:36,307 --> 00:41:39,586
I checked the portraits
for the embroideress.

704
00:41:40,026 --> 00:41:42,907
And I increasingly felt
that something was wrong.

705
00:41:43,707 --> 00:41:45,427
I was stuck on the ship for days,

706
00:41:45,506 --> 00:41:47,466
so this matter was delayed.

707
00:41:47,947 --> 00:41:48,947
After returning,

708
00:41:49,747 --> 00:41:52,546
I asked Wu An to investigate Gu Songju.

709
00:41:53,586 --> 00:41:54,947
You investigate another person for me.

710
00:41:55,227 --> 00:41:56,307
Yes.

711
00:41:56,827 --> 00:41:59,666
The concubine of officer Xu Zhiyang

712
00:42:00,227 --> 00:42:01,347
is named Gu Songju.

713
00:42:01,867 --> 00:42:04,146
Send someone to Qizhou

714
00:42:04,466 --> 00:42:06,146
to investigate her background.

715
00:42:06,347 --> 00:42:08,986
Also, keep a close eye on her.

716
00:42:09,626 --> 00:42:10,867
Find out where she has been,

717
00:42:11,106 --> 00:42:12,186
and whom she has met.

718
00:42:12,427 --> 00:42:13,267
Take down every detail.

719
00:42:13,947 --> 00:42:16,227
Before my people returned from Qizhou,

720
00:42:17,267 --> 00:42:18,707
you have exposed yourself.

721
00:42:19,466 --> 00:42:21,867
At first, I thought
what I had experienced lately

722
00:42:22,387 --> 00:42:25,146
was caused by Cripple Liu
who just got out of jail.

723
00:42:26,506 --> 00:42:28,747
When Wu An saw you two
having a secret meeting,

724
00:42:29,186 --> 00:42:32,787
I connect these strange things together.

725
00:42:34,387 --> 00:42:36,506
You have been working hard
on these matters.

726
00:42:37,347 --> 00:42:38,787
Now it's all in vain.

727
00:42:39,066 --> 00:42:40,387
What do you feel now?

728
00:42:40,907 --> 00:42:41,827
Mr. Wu.

729
00:42:42,907 --> 00:42:44,106
The victory is not yet decided.

730
00:42:45,026 --> 00:42:47,986
What makes you think it's all in vain?

731
00:42:49,466 --> 00:42:51,267
You are so persistent,

732
00:42:52,787 --> 00:42:54,986
because you feel guilty
for Rulan, right?

733
00:42:56,666 --> 00:42:59,307
Can you sleep well at night?

734
00:43:01,827 --> 00:43:02,787
And you?

735
00:43:05,186 --> 00:43:07,747
Can you live in peace

736
00:43:09,026 --> 00:43:10,747
after harming so many innocent people?

737
00:43:11,347 --> 00:43:12,186
Meng Wan.

738
00:43:12,666 --> 00:43:15,066
You brought an inquisitor here,
but so what?

739
00:43:16,947 --> 00:43:18,986
For such a trivial love affair,

740
00:43:19,586 --> 00:43:21,626
do you really think
the court will attach importance to it?

741
00:43:27,787 --> 00:43:29,066
Rulan will not die in vain.

742
00:43:31,466 --> 00:43:33,427
I will make you pay the price.

743
00:43:34,787 --> 00:43:37,387
We'll see, Madame Xu.

744
00:43:41,778 --> 00:43:48,120
(Goodliness)

