00:44:12,267 --> 00:44:14,707
Madam, it's late.

746
00:44:16,707 --> 00:44:17,387
Xiangzhu.

747
00:44:19,387 --> 00:44:22,986
Is the night wind in Huaizhou cold?

748
00:44:23,947 --> 00:44:25,787
Or is the night wind
in the capital cold?

749
00:44:26,707 --> 00:44:28,747
Madam, I don't know.

750
00:44:32,066 --> 00:44:33,707
Compared to the capital,

751
00:44:35,227 --> 00:44:38,827
it is danker in Huaizhou.

752
00:44:45,387 --> 00:44:48,026
I don't know if I still have a chance
to go back to the capital.

753
00:44:53,907 --> 00:44:55,466
Even if I can go back,

754
00:44:57,227 --> 00:45:01,427
I'm afraid
I can't feel familiar anymore.

755
00:45:32,466 --> 00:45:33,947
We split ways?

756
00:45:35,387 --> 00:45:36,506
Can we?

757
00:45:37,066 --> 00:45:38,986
At this point, it's hard to say.

758
00:45:41,427 --> 00:45:42,867
Maybe we chose the wrong path

759
00:45:44,387 --> 00:45:45,986
from the beginning.

760
00:45:47,186 --> 00:45:49,626
Should I still go to the eastern market

761
00:45:49,827 --> 00:45:51,066
to look for that guy?

762
00:45:52,026 --> 00:45:53,347
Just put it aside.

763
00:46:08,186 --> 00:46:09,026
Who is it?

764
00:46:09,347 --> 00:46:11,466
Madame Xu, it's me.
Please open the door.

765
00:46:18,747 --> 00:46:19,546
What happened?

766
00:46:19,787 --> 00:46:21,546
It's done.

767
00:46:21,986 --> 00:46:23,066
What's done?

768
00:46:23,347 --> 00:46:24,347
I wanted to ask you.

769
00:46:24,787 --> 00:46:25,986
When I returned in the afternoon,

770
00:46:26,186 --> 00:46:27,466
I was so worried.

771
00:46:27,827 --> 00:46:29,186
But just after nightfall,

772
00:46:29,387 --> 00:46:31,106
someone from the Ning Mansion

773
00:46:31,307 --> 00:46:32,986
paid me lots of money.

774
00:46:33,387 --> 00:46:35,907
Mrs. Ning has chosen Huai Embroidery.

775
00:46:36,146 --> 00:46:38,347
They asked us to finish it
as fast as possible.

776
00:46:38,747 --> 00:46:39,586
Well,

777
00:46:39,787 --> 00:46:41,546
did you go to the Ning Mansion again

778
00:46:41,986 --> 00:46:44,106
and say something to Mrs. Ning?

779
00:46:47,586 --> 00:46:48,506
Mr. Liu.

780
00:46:49,146 --> 00:46:51,427
You need to find that guy tomorrow.

781
00:47:03,427 --> 00:47:04,106
Mr. Lou.

782
00:47:06,827 --> 00:47:09,186
Greetings, Mr. Lou. I'm Meng Wan.

783
00:47:09,626 --> 00:47:12,787
Please seek justice for Lin Rulan.

784
00:47:23,267 --> 00:47:23,986
Sit.

785
00:47:24,626 --> 00:47:25,707
Thank you.

